freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Hot flashes even in a 54 degree house. Ice storm, no electricity.

Random rashes on upper arms, chest area, thighs, neck and head. Not all at once, but just random. Also have occasional hot flashes. Also have almost had wheezing, a slight cough, havent had to use my inhaler yet.
Random temperature fluctuations. Achy muscles. Fatigue.
